  "title": "Operations Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Provide the leadership management, and vision necessary to ensure that the Company has the proper operational controls, administrative and reporting procedures. To put human resource systems in place to effectively manage and grow the organization and operating efficiencies.</li><li>Establishing plans, budgets, and results measurements; allocating resources; reviewing progress.</li><li>Coordinate with landlords, vendors, and contractors on all operational matters.</li><li>Warehouse & Inventory management import and export logistics to maximise efficiency and accuracy.</li><li>Coordinate IT maintenance and software updates by liaising with IT vendors.</li><li>Ensure all repairs and maintenance are up to standards and within budget.</li><li>Research and apply strategies that will help to support our manpower needs.</li><li>Lead and manage Office Admin and Service Admin.</li><li>Establish and maintain effective working relationships within the team and the company.</li><li>Manage day to day agendas, calendars, coordinate and schedule appointments, internal and external business meetings, travel arrangements: flight reservation, hotel accommodation for the General Manager.</li><li>Communicate, follow-up and liaise with internal and external stakeholders.</li><li>Handle travel arrangements: flight reservation, hotel accommodation, visa applications etc.</li><li>Carry out any other tasks assigned to you by the General Manager of Steinway Gallery.</li></ul>",
