    "description": "<p>C. Melchers GmbH &amp; Co., Singapore Branch was established in 1954 to coordinate the trading activities in South East Asia. &nbsp;&nbsp;Independent companies were set up in all ASEAN countries and Sri Lanka. &nbsp;Singapore serves as a trading- and service-hub for the region. &nbsp;We market, sell, distribute and service products such as technical materials, machinery and equipment, laboratory instruments, aviation technology, pharmaceutical products, valves and pressure vessels, even pianos, luxury goods and watches. &nbsp;We also provide corporate services and delegate office support.</p>",
